        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">PHI-safe by design. First names and appointment times only — never diagnosis or insurance details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex justify-end"><div class="rounded-2xl rounded-br-sm bg-teal-600 text-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm max-w-xs">Hi Alex, you're checked in for your 2:30 PM appointment. We'll text you with any updates.</div></div>
